desc:
Skips questions based on the answer to another question: 
    <div>Example:
    <code class="configCodeBlock">
    "skipQuestions": [
      {"OnQuestion": "PathChoice",
        "IfValues": {
          "FieldName": "PathChoice",
          "DoesNotInclude": true,
          "Values": [
            "refi"
          ]
        },
        "QuestionToSkip": [
          "CashoutPurpose"
        ]
      }    
    ]
    </code>
    </div>
